title: The President Is High On Steroids, Cobra Kai Is About Class 10.6.20

description:
In episode 730, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian, Private Parts Unknown, and 420 Day Fiance co-host Sofiya Alexandra to discuss Trump's covid-19 shenanigans, The Secret: Dare to Dream, Cobra Kai, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Secret Service Agents Take Bullet From President
  2. The Trump White House as a Covid-19 Hot Spot
  3. Trump Didn’t Disclose First Positive Covid-19 Test While Awaiting a Second Test on Thursday
  4. 'Starting to feel good.' Trump releases new video from Walter Reed amid COVID battle
  5. Trump in Walter Reed Photo-Op Appears to Sign Blank Paper to Show He's Well and 'Relentless'
  6. WATCH: Burial - Archangel
